                <h1>Assault charges are served upon a Duke professor, his attorney asserts the ‘allegations are false’</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/d7836b0d-c1c0-49e0-b3ea-11291e047b9e.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Ranjan&#x20;Sudan,&#x20;professor&#x20;and&#x20;vice&#x20;chair&#x20;of&#x20;education&#x20;in&#x20;the&#x20;department&#x20;of&#x20;surgery&#x20;at&#x20;the&#x20;School&#x20;of&#x20;Medicine&#x20;and&#x20;Duke&#x20;Health&#x20;general&#x20;surgeon.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Ranjan Sudan, professor and vice chair of education in the department of surgery at the School of Medicine and Duke Health general surgeon.</p>

